metadata.name: January 2
metadata.description:
The new me is always reborn, acquiring true beauty and true strangeness.

This artwork is a video piece that is the result of my editing, collaging, and intricate combination of "beautiful" and "strange" images produced by AI.This is reminiscent of my early style when I first started creating crypto art in April 2019.I create them one by one, carefully creating them and piling them up high in the sky, thinking deeply once again about the meaning of creating art.
